    <scopecontent id="aspace_hzc210077n520as95436414040788">
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>10 pocket-sized sketchbooks of Harriet and Ernest Longfellow containing charcoal and watercolor sketches, predominantly panoramic views of European and Middle Eastern architectural ruins, landscape scenery, and a number of figure drawings; and 3 notecards describing the sketchbooks and sketches.</p>
    </scopecontent>
    <altformavail id="aspace_hzc210077n530as88396325454248">
      <head>Existence and Location of Copies</head>
